user.biography: The super fun text-based life simulator by @candywriter for iOS & Android. Tag us w/ your favorite screenshots! We 💛 Bitizens! 🙌

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by BitLife on August 11, 2021. May be a cartoon of screen and text that says ''dby u/the_ Countess Of_BR didn't see any other option... had to become friends with him Harry Potter Friend Profile Relationship: Friend YearsFriends:<1 Years Friends: Gender: Male Age:5 Occupation: Primary School Student Relationship Looks Smarts Craziness Change our status BiTLiFE'.

node.text: As long as I don't end up the Ron Weasley of the group then, yeah, I'm gonna be best friends with Harry Potter. ⚡️

node.text: This is so unfair, I call BS! 🤬

node.text: How many of your subjects have you killed, Bitizens? There's only a little while left to finish the challenge! ❤️

node.text: Seriously, Bitizens. What better day to finish the dictionary? Or, you know, at least "If You Give a Mouse a Cookie." #NationalBookLoversDay 📚
